Package: ethiodate
Type: Package
Title: Ethiopian Date Conversion and Arithmetic in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Gutama Girja", "Urago",
      email = "girjagutama@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")
    )
  )
Description: This package provides a robust and efficient solution for working 
    with Ethiopian dates. It can seamlessly convert to and from Gregorian dates. 
    It ensures lightning-fast computations thanks to the `{Rcpp}` package that 
    enables the integration of high-performance C++ code. It has built-in checks 
    for leap years and the 13th month (Pagume).
